{
  "stem": "5758.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You must show them that you are OK, fit to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we knew that once you are being put on the side there, in that side, you are going to die, because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we knew-- we-- we-- we-- people were talking about the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We heard about chimneys, although I must say, always from third persons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was never somebody who was there in person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And somehow or other, if you feel that this can be maybe an imagination, maybe, there is always, if you're an optimist like I was, I am always-- I have always been an optimist.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I felt I will live, and I must live, then-- and that there is-- being an optimist, I had hope.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had hope to survive, and I wanted to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wanted to survive to be able to see my family again and tell them what has happened to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it-- it was a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this optimism that I have, I think kept me also alive very much.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the-- the whole attitude, I knew that some people just could not-- did not have that attitude I had, and they did not last very long.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were selected.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They collapsed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Some of them, I remember, was-- I woke up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In the next bunk of mine, there was an older man who died in-- at nighttime.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, he just didn't wake up anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I knew he gave up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He always said, I know I'm going to die here, when we spoke to each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He always said, I know we'll never come out of here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We are finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, with an attitude like this, here, I feel that he talked himself into dying, I believe.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
